html code that goes through five pictures from a folder on buttonclick. the button is green and says "next" on it. the picture number is placed on the top right of the webpage in green. and when it gets to the last picture and the user presses the next button make the web page display the total number of pictures, the time it took to get through them all, and a message saying "Gee willikers"
